---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Yuvraj Biswal">
  <div class="space-y-10">
    <section>
      <h1 class="text-[25px] font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)] mb-5" style="font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', Inter, sans-serif;">Me</h1>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I'm mostly into physics, maths and programming.
          Currently working at <a href="https://dognosis.tech">Dognosis</a>.
        </p>

        <p>At the time of writing, my interests are:</p>

        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1.5 ml-5">
          <li><strong>Programming:</strong> Systems, CLI tools, Backend, Deep Learning, and distributed systems.</li>
          <li><strong>Physics:</strong> Quantum mechanics, astrophysics.</li>
          <li><strong>Math:</strong> Calculus,Statistics,linear algebra.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-[22px] font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', Inter, sans-serif;">Experience</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-lg">
              <img src="/dognosis_logo.jpg" alt="Dognosis Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)]">
                <a href="https://dognosis.tech">Dognosis</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--sky-700)]">Software Engineer</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1.5">July 2025 – Present</p>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
                Working on Rust backend development for the Dognosis API pipeline and cancer report analysis portal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white border border-[var(--border-color)] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-lg">
              <img src="/stealth.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)]">
                <a href="https://systemsway.com">Systemsway</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--sky-700)]">Software Engineer</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1.5">August 2025 – September 2025</p>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
                Developed Go backend services and infrastructure for scalable cloud applications.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-lg">
              <img src="/superteam_logo.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)]">
                <a href="https://superteam.fun">SuperteamIn</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--sky-700)]">Web3 Fellow</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1.5">July 2025 – November 2025</p>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
                Selected as a Solana fellow to build on Solana blockchain. Developing decentralized applications using Rust and Anchor framework.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-lg">
              <img src="/shabzak_logo.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)]">
                <a href="https://shabzak.tech">Shabzak Tech</a>
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--sky-700)]">Web Dev Instructor</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1.5">July 2024 – October 2024</p>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
                Designed and delivered Vue.js courses from beginner to advanced levels with project-based curriculum.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-[22px] font-medium text-[var(--slate-700)] mb-3" style="font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', Inter, sans-serif;">Feedback</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
        Have feedback on my portfolio? <a href="mailto:yuvrajbiswalofficial@gmail.com?subject=Portfolio Feedback">Let me know →</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
